      "source": [
        "## Initial Data Loading and Scope Filtering\n",
        "\n",
        "The cleaned dataset is loaded from the Excel file specified in the environment variable. A predefined list of Thanas is then excluded from the analysis. These excluded values represent locations that are not part of the intended analytical scope for this experiment.\n",
        "\n",
        "Records with missing `Thana` values are also removed because the location field is essential for all subsequent grouping, classification, and percentage calculations."
      ],
      "id": "f63a7f4a"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "path = os.getenv(\"CLEANED_DATASET_PATH\")\n",
        "if path is None:\n",
        "    raise ValueError(\"CLEANED_DATASET_PATH not set\")\n",
        "\n",
        "df = pd.read_excel(path)\n",
        "\n",
        "values = [\"Senbag\", \"Shahjadpur\", \"Barkal\", \"Chandina\", \"Chatkhil\",\n",
        "          \"Chouddagram\", \"Companyganj\", \"Cox's Bazar Sadar\",\n",
        "          \"Cumilla Adarsha Sadar\", \"Jorargonj\", \"Kawkhali\",\n",
        "          \"Khagrachhari Sadar\", \"Kobirhat\", \"Manikchhari\",\n",
        "          \"Matiranga\", \"Moheshkhali\", \"Muradnagar\", \"Nabinagar\",\n",
        "          \"Noakhali Sadar\", \"Ramgarh\", \"Rangamati Sadar\",\n",
        "          \"Shahrasti\", \"Sonagazi\", \"Ukhia\", \"Hatia\", \"Chakaria\"]\n",
        "\n",
        "df = df.loc[~df['Thana'].isin(values)]\n",
        "\n",
        "df.dropna(subset=[\"Thana\"], inplace=True)"
      ],
      "id": "65f2babf",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## City Corporation and Outside City Corporation Classification\n",
        "\n",
        "Two reference lists are created to classify Thanas into two analytical groups:\n",
        "\n",
        "- **Inside City Corporation**, representing Thanas within the City Corporation area.\n",
        "- **Outside City Corporation**, representing Thanas outside the City Corporation but still within the analysis boundary.\n",
        "\n",
        "These lists are later used to split the dataset and calculate separate summaries for each group."
      ],
      "id": "2b8698f5"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "thanas_outside_cc = [\"Mirsharai\", \"Fatikchhari\", \"Raozan\", \"Sitakunda\", \"Hathazari\", \"Boalkhali\", \"Patiya\", \"Chandanaish\", \"Sandwip\", \"Rangunia\", \"Anowara\", \"Satkania\", \"Banshkhali\", \"Lohagara\"]\n",
        "thanas_in_cc = [\"Bayejid Bostami\", \"Chandgaon\", \"Bakalia\", \"Kotwali\", \"Double Mooring\", \"Patenga\", \"Chittagong Port\", \"Halishahar\", \"Pahartali\", \"Khulshi\", \"Panchlaish\"]"
      ],
      "id": "721af1e5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Standardizing Thana Names\n",
        "\n",
        "Some records contain alternative spellings, informal names, administrative variants, or localized labels for the same Thana. A mapping dictionary is used to standardize these names into the classification labels used in the analysis.\n",
        "\n",
        "This step is important because inconsistent naming can split the same geographic area into multiple categories and distort count-based summaries."
      ],
      "id": "97e45cd7"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "mapping = {\n",
        "    \"Firingibazar\": \"Kotwali\",\n",
        "    \"EPZ\": \"Chittagong Port\",\n",
        "    \"Lalkhan Bazar\": \"Khulshi\",\n",
        "    \"Patharghata\": \"Kotwali\",\n",
        "    \"Kaptai\": \"Rangunia\",\n",
        "    \"Fouzdarhat\": \"Sitakunda\",\n",
        "    \"New Mooring\": \"Chittagong Port\",\n",
        "    \"Agrabad\": \"Double Mooring\",\n",
        "    \"Karnaphuli\": \"Patiya\",\n",
        "    \"Bhujpur\": \"Fatikchhari\",\n",
        "    \"Chawk Bazar\": \"Panchlaish\",\n",
        "    \"Bandar\": \"Chittagong Port\",\n",
        "    \"Anwara\":\"Anowara\",\n",
        "    \"Sadarghat\": \"Patiya\",\n",
        "    \"Akbar Shah\":\"Pahartali\",\n",
        "    \"Bayazid Bostami\":\"Bayejid Bostami\",\n",
        "    \"Bandarban Sadar\":\"Satkania\"\n",
        "}"
