      "source": [
        "## Age Group Creation\n",
        "\n",
        "A new categorical variable, `Age Group`, is created using the following rule:\n",
        "\n",
        "- `<=30` for records where age is less than or equal to 30.\n",
        "- `>30` for records where age is greater than 30.\n",
        "\n",
        "This age grouping supports comparison of younger and older population segments across Thanas and City Corporation classifications."
      ],
      "id": "ffac78a3"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "df[\"Age Group\"] = np.where(df[\"Age\"] <= 30, \"<=30\", \">30\")\n",
        "\n",
        "df[\"Age Group\"].value_counts()\n",
        "\n",
        "df.groupby([\"Age Group\", \"Thana\"]).size()"
      ],
