      "source": [
        "## Creating City Corporation and Outside City Corporation Subsets\n",
        "\n",
        "The dataset is divided into two filtered DataFrames:\n",
        "\n",
        "- `df_cc`: records belonging to Thanas inside the City Corporation.\n",
        "- `df_outside`: records belonging to Thanas outside the City Corporation.\n",
        "\n",
        "Creating these subsets simplifies downstream calculations and keeps the analysis more readable."
      ],
      "id": "51aeb53f"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# Pre-filter DataFrames for cleaner execution\n",
        "df_cc = df[df[\"Thana\"].isin(thanas_in_cc)]\n",
        "df_outside = df[df[\"Thana\"].isin(thanas_outside_cc)]"
      ],
      "id": "5b4855ae",
