      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Record Counts by Classification and Thana\n",
        "\n",
        "This section calculates total records inside the City Corporation, total records outside the City Corporation, and individual Thana-level counts for both groups."
      ],
      "id": "39e46b0f"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# Total records in City Corporation\n",
        "total_cc_records = len(df_cc)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Total records for each individual thana in City Corporation\n",
        "thana_counts_in_cc = df_cc[\"Thana\"].value_counts()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Total records Outside City Corporation\n",
        "total_outside_cc_records = len(df_outside)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Total records for each individual thana outside City Corporation\n",
