      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Age Group Counts by Classification and Thana\n",
        "\n",
        "The following grouped summaries are calculated:\n",
        "\n",
        "- Total City Corporation records by age group.\n",
        "- City Corporation Thana-level records by age group.\n",
        "- Outside City Corporation Thana-level records by age group.\n",
        "- Total outside City Corporation records by age group.\n",
        "\n",
        "These grouped outputs support both aggregate and location-specific demographic interpretation."
      ],
      "id": "cd020083"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# Total records in City Corporation grouped by Age Group\n",
        "cc_records_by_age = df_cc.groupby(\"Age Group\").size()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Total records for each thana in CC grouped by Age Group\n",
        "cc_thana_records_by_age = df_cc.groupby([\"Thana\", \"Age Group\"]).size()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Total records for each thana outside CC grouped by Age Group\n",
        "outside_thana_records_by_age = df_outside.groupby([\"Thana\", \"Age Group\"]).size()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Total records outside CC grouped by Age Group\n",
        "outside_cc_records_by_age = df_outside.groupby(\"Age Group\").size()"
      ],
